Class RBClockModifier.RBClockModifierToken

java.lang.Object
com.rb.biz.guice.RBClockModifier.RBClockModifierToken
Enclosing class:
RBClockModifier
public static final class RBClockModifier.RBClockModifierToken
extends java.lang.Object
Unusually, this class holds nothing and does nothing. It exists as a safety mechanism to prevent unintentionally overwriting the global RBClock. See RBClock.overwriteCurrentTime(com.rb.biz.guice.RBClockModifier.RBClockModifierToken, java.time.LocalDateTime) for more.
